title: Grateful Dead Live at Frost Amphitheatre on 1983-08-20

description:
Set I
Alabama Getaway >

Comment

Bob Weir - Guitar

Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
